snippet.title: Gen Z Reacts To Wednesday & The Addams Family! | REACT
snippet.description:
With Wednesday becoming a massive hit, we thought we would go back and have Gen Z react to The Addams Family throughout the years, including the original Addams Family show, Addams Family Values, and the Addams Family Musical! 
Watch more episodes of React here! https://reactmedia.co/34NyMYX

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VWrhIFVoWn8

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NakTu_VZxJ0
